}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "P/N:FKHU2011712 2003/01/20" and "USB2.0 7Port HUB 1.7" is silkscreened on the top of the board. :A sticker with "DUB-H7(1.7" and the S/N ("S/N:0512PH112951") is affixed to the bottom of the board. The manufacturer of this device is presumed to be the Taiwan based [http://www.mct.com.tw '''Magic Control Technology Corp.''' ('''MCT''')].
The silkscreened text is identical to that of the [[Targus PAUH212U]], which is a UH7U v1.7. This device is presumed to have the same '''MCT''' model.
